## Design system — Brand Navy Dark

Token Tailwind 4 in `apps/web/src/index.css` via `@theme inline`. **MAI** classi `zinc-*` o `blue-600` dirette — sempre `sc-*`.

```
Sfondo:    bg-sc-bg (#07101f)        Card:    bg-sc-surface (#0d1c30)     Elevated: bg-sc-elevated (#132844)
Primary:   bg-sc-primary (#3FA9F5)   Hover:   bg-sc-primary-deep (#0B5ED7)
Accent:    bg-sc-accent (#FF7A00)    Navy:    bg-sc-navy (#0A2540)

Text:      text-sc-text (#f0f2f5)    Sec:     text-sc-text-secondary (#b8c5d4)
Muted:     text-sc-text-muted        Dim:     text-sc-text-dim

Success:   text-sc-success           Warning: text-sc-warning              Danger: text-sc-danger

Bordi:     border-sc-primary/12      Input:   border-sc-primary/20
Focus:     ring-sc-ring/25 + focus:border-sc-primary/40
```

**Pattern obbligatori:**

- `rounded-xl` per card/input/bottoni; `rounded-2xl` per card grandi (auth, modali principali)
- Font: DM Sans (Google Fonts, definito in `@theme` + `index.html`)
- Sidebar: `bg-sc-surface/80 backdrop-blur-xl border-sc-primary/10`
- Bottone primario: `bg-sc-primary text-white shadow-lg shadow-sc-primary/20 hover:bg-sc-primary-deep`
- Input: `bg-sc-bg border-sc-primary/15 rounded-xl focus:border-sc-primary/40 focus:ring-2 focus:ring-sc-ring/25`

**Principi UX:**

- Stato sempre visibile con colore inequivocabile
- Zero ambiguita sulla versione (numero + timestamp + hash troncato)
- Feedback entro 200ms per azioni UI
- Dark mode only (coerenza con sito marketing www.liveworksapp.com)
- Densita informativa alta — utenti target: tecnici AV esperti

## Logo / brand

- **Sorgente:** `icons/Logo Live Slide Center.jpg` (file unico in git).
- **Pipeline:** `apps/web/scripts/generate-brand-icons.mjs` (devDependency `sharp`) eseguita da `prebuild`/`predev` su `@slidecenter/web`.
- **Output:** `apps/web/public/` (favicon-16x16.png, favicon-32x32.png, apple-touch-icon.png, pwa-192x192.png, pwa-512x512.png, logo-live-slide-center.jpg).
- **In React:** sempre `AppBrandLogo` da `src/components/AppBrandLogo.tsx` + `t('app.displayName')` per il wordmark. NON duplicare `<img src="...">`.

## Error Boundary

- Ogni feature wrappata in `<ErrorBoundary moduleName="...">` nel router
- `<AppErrorBoundary>` globale in `main.tsx`
- MAI swallowing silenzioso in upload, sync, pairing, download — usare `reportError(err, { tag, extra })` di `lib/telemetry.ts`

## Dual mode cloud / desktop (Sprint J-O)

- La SPA `apps/web` e' **identica** in cloud Vercel e in build desktop Tauri. Discriminator: `import.meta.env.VITE_BACKEND_MODE === 'desktop'`.
- Helpers in `apps/web/src/lib/backend-mode.ts`: `getBackendMode()`, `isRunningInTauri()`, `getBackendDescriptor()`.
- Auth: `auth-provider.tsx` esporta `CloudAuthProvider` (Supabase session) + `DesktopAuthProvider` (session fittizia, vedi `desktop-fake-session.ts`).
- Backend client: sempre via `apps/web/src/lib/supabase.ts` o `lib/backend-client.ts` — questi auto-target il server Rust locale in modalita desktop.
- Realtime: `lib/realtime-client.ts` astrazione `subscribeToTopic(topic, options)` — cloud usa `supabase.channel(...)`, desktop usa long-poll Sprint N3 `/events/stream`.
- Backend status: hook `useBackendStatus()` in `lib/use-backend-status.ts` (5 stati: cloud-online/cloud-offline/lan-connected/standalone/loading) → `BackendModeBadge` nella sidebar.
- Update banner desktop: `<DesktopUpdateBanner>` in `RootLayout` (no-op in cloud; check al boot + ogni 30 min in Tauri).

## Anti-pattern (vietati)

- Stringhe IT hardcoded in JSX (vedi `03-i18n.mdc`)
- `useState` settato sincrono nel body di `useEffect` (lint React 19)
- Filter Realtime globale tipo `status=eq.ready` su tabelle condivise (riceveresti eventi di TUTTI i tenant)
- Dipendenza implicita su `tenant_id` lato client (RLS filtra automaticamente)
- Class Tailwind `zinc-*` / `blue-600` (usare token `sc-*`)
- `apps/player/` — NON deve esistere; il Room Player e' route `/sala/:token` in `apps/web/`
